    "objectID": "index.html#summary",
    "href": "index.html#summary",
    "title": "Educational Attainment in Los Angeles County",
    "section": "Summary",
    "text": "Summary\nThis project maps bachelor’s degree attainment across Los Angeles County census tracts using American Community Survey data.\nThe goal is to make educational inequality visible at the neighborhood level. County-wide averages can hide large local differences, but a tract-level map helps show where human-capital attainment is concentrated and where it may lag behind."
